<section id="connecting-online" class="connecting-online py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16 bg-white">
  <article class="max-w-sm sm:max-w-xl md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 sm:mb-6 md:mb-8 text-center sm:text-left">Connecting Online</h1>

    <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-5 md:space-y-6 text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg">
      <p>
        There are many ways to get involved in the Australian Ruby community. If you're looking for something online -
        where you can ask questions and keep on top of the latest happenings - there's our
        <%= link_to "Slack workspace", "/slack", class: "text-ruby-red hover:text-red-400 transition-colors underline" %>.
      </p>

      <p>
        We also have talks from our previous events - both conferences and meetings available on
        <%= link_to "YouTube", "/videos", class: "text-ruby-red hover:text-red-400 transition-colors underline" %>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 sm:mt-8 md:mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 justify-center sm:justify-start">
      <%= link_to "Join our Slack", "/slack", class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-ruby-red hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-medium py-2 px-4 sm:py-3 sm:px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-md text-sm sm:text-base" %>
      <%= link_to "Watch Videos", "/videos", class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center border border-ruby-red text-ruby-red hover:bg-ruby-red hover:text-white font-medium py-2 px-4 sm:py-3 sm:px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm sm:text-base" %>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
